ơ chí gia - 初至家</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C3%B4ng/author-rfaS1tOCWjWB9PkLJ5MHxw">Nguyễn Thông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%91-Ho%C3%A0nh/S%C6%B0-Trang-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/poem-PtxbpqyAmQaHc_aZyw_JvA">Sư Trang đạo thượng - 師莊道上</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%91-Ho%C3%A0nh/author-7fpzU7wRIKA3ExH3sUtNHg">Cố Hoành</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-T%E1%BA%A3i/Thanh-Vi%E1%BB%85n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-s%C4%A9-d%C6%B0%E1%BB%A1ng-h%E1%BA%A1c-gi%E1%BA%A3n/poem-vC4s4r9LQE415yd9MJhzAA">Thanh Viễn đạo sĩ dưỡng hạc giản - 清遠道士養鶴澗</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-T%E1%BA%A3i/author-MUc7SXkTGCBX3NA_zoUBjA">Tiền Tải</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/U-gi%E1%BA%A3n-tuy%E1%BB%81n/poem-EWXqNfXDGvE8oGnx69xyyQ">U giản tuyền - 幽澗泉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Vi%C3%AAn-Minh-vi%C3%AAn/poem-vFKM4EqxbQHheoXIOW6LTQ">Viên Minh viên - 圓明園</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br></div>	</div>
